br />\n屬瑣屑無聊、無理纏擾或濫用程序。因此，版權審裁處暫准命令 Neway 支付香港卡拉歌<br />\n曲版權聯盟就版權授權費的計算程序而引致或相關的訟費 （金额按對訟當事人基準評<br />\n定）"},{"pid":"1a4b0635911c98c2dbeef9f6f6ed8cdd4414491b","tid":2515500,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"UA&mdash;&gt;Neway&mdash;&gt;下一個係？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9349b86048a83520a07f9a069dc909ba543def","tid":2515500,"uid":151294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877dd828ae6c75de3832c387ef8dd18fdcdd29a5","tid":2515500,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c51ca86c59a438c83849e200f0b75e9be5f165b7","tid":2515500,"uid":151294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04380d53937d74094f7d9a096849baeb8a9e3a6e","tid":2515500,"uid":5686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"有幾弱智先會咁隊自己嘅大客？<br />\n清佢盤九成都未輪到佢收錢啦，<br />\n隊死Neway 佢有咩著數？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"2010年5月，HKRIA旗下的成員組織 &mdash; 香港卡拉歌曲版權盟有限公司(HKKLA)正式成立，負責管理索尼音樂娛樂、華納唱片、百代唱片及環球唱片的卡拉OK音像版權。<br />\n<br />\nNeway 從來都唔係HKRIA 嘅大客之一，啱啱仲要打咗場官司"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"香港仲有幾多卡場比佢收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"另外，乜撚野係卡場？？？？？？？？？？？？？？"}]}